{"tid":709723,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯母親：他承受痛苦","createTime":"2018-06-20T08:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:45:35.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4ddf181be1a82500a92b6928e38982033e8cfa","tid":709723,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"美斯母親：他承受痛苦"},{"pid":"8d5fa6bbe66a0001c932c6d27c97f3a1055fcd27","tid":709723,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=f1ak%2FKx76gFv0bJ44sDKYKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4af600cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿根廷球王美斯的母親接受訪問時替兒子打氣，道出兒子的辛酸，愛子之情盡溢言表。"},{"pid":"ab5bc7c6e7bb745133917c94f95ecaeb2426404a","tid":709723,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"阿根廷球星美斯（Lionel Messi）背負國家隊奪冠希望，首戰對冰島射失12碼成為焦點，壓力之大可想而知，但出自母親希莉雅之口，就更加令人動容。希莉雅罕有地接受阿根廷電視台訪問時說：「我經常看到他在承受痛苦和哭泣，尤其當人們說他不想替國家隊效力時，對他傷害更大。」"},{"pid":"0af46e23b1d52e8be48168159e635d4922c6b8d5","tid":709723,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"希莉雅表示沒有人比美斯更想奪得世界盃，「他的心態比以前更放鬆和冷靜。我祝他好運，希望他照顧好自己，享受場上的每一個時刻，家人們都支持他。」她也自然流露對兒子的愛，「也許我不該這麼說，但我真的願意用一切，換取他拿到世界盃冠軍。」<br />\n<br />\n美斯是希莉雅4個孩子之一，她承認美斯不光是最好的兒子，還是最好的爸爸。"},{"pid":"8727d7c4144e717d1c05d2cfb1eb02e8770ec5da","tid":709723,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7450ac0e11a57d54992eb44fdaf627ddb7ca5657","tid":709723,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"post都唔識貼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d4b7021079b05ff0aa5ea8104095838b00589e","tid":709723,"uid":155902,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0